WOlfblade::

She walked over to Malice and sat down next to him. "You sleep ok?"
She sipped her glass and yawned, "Oh, and thanks for what you did 
last night. Just do me the favor and tell no one of it."

wrote:
> OOC- If Wolfblade would look over her head, she would see Malice 
snoozing away.  And don't worry, I make lots of mistakes when I'm

> Malice snored audibly, but not loudly.  He would occasionally roll 
onto one side, but generally slept well.  A few megacycles later, his 
alarm went off, and he grundgingly crawled out of his hammock.  He 
slowly made his way to the mess hall to find a cup of energon.  He 
noticed it was exceedingly quiet.  That was due to the fact that he 
was oblivious to everyone else until he had at least one glass of 
refined energon.
